nnected to the network can serve as help to field agents, distraction for the security or a deadly weapon!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/687340/extras/78ddd83ef08f80cc9492d94bde085c51.avif?t=1667207807\" width=612 height=382 /></span>",
